# UI-harness baseline screenshots go through Git LFS to keep the repo clone
# size sane. The top-level `screenshots/*.png` files (title.png, gameplay.png,
# gameover.png, cover-v2-candidate.png) pre-date this policy and stay as raw
# blobs to avoid a history rewrite. Only new harness output is LFS-tracked.
screenshots/ui-harness/**/*.png filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
